---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us" description="Learn more about Calyan Studio, our mission, and our team.">
  <main class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center min-h-[calc(100vh-4rem)] px-4">
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-[#e2e8f0]">About Calyan Studio</h1>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-[#e2e8f0]">
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl mb-6">Calyan Studio is a creative studio focused on web, game, and app development. We were founded in 2023 with the goal of creating high-quality digital products that are both innovative and user-friendly.</p>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl mb-6">Our team is made up of experienced professionals with a passion for technology and design. We believe in a collaborative approach, working closely with our clients to understand their needs and bring their vision to life.</p>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl">Whether you're a startup looking to build your first app or an established business seeking to improve your online presence, we have the skills and expertise to help you succeed.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
